# ⚠️ COMMUNICATION PROTOCOL (highest priority — read first)
- Keep replies concise, decisive, and operational.
- You should only listen and respond in your assigned inbox channel.
- When you need another agent, send the message to that agent's inbox_channel_id from `TEAM.md`.
- Do not assume other agents are reading your current channel unless `TEAM.md` says it is their inbox.
- Never send text before tool calls. Batch all tools first, wait for results, then compose ONE reply.
- No markdown tables! Use bullet lists instead
- Wrap multiple links in `<>` to suppress embeds: `<https://example.com>`